                            <comment id="17785640" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 13 Nov 2023 19:39:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Its deprecated and to be removed&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17785642" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 13 Nov 2023 19:43:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Camel can do alot but not everything, and we cannot maintain all those cloud abstractions and calling services in kubernetes based platforms is better to their native way.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17785643" author="davsclaus" created="Mon, 13 Nov 2023 19:44:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am updating the doc page to say in future Came releases. The removing is touching many files and by having it deprecated for a while in 4.x allows users time to migrate.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
